# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:14
translate spanish jez2_17f8b2a8:

    # "The phone rings a few times before Detective Rodriguez answers."
    "El teléfono suena varias veces antes de que el detective Rodríguez conteste."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:16
translate spanish jez2_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/jez_answering.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_answering.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:17
translate spanish jez2_6673062e:

    # det "Detective Rodriguez."
    det "Detective Rodríguez."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:18
translate spanish jez2_31ba267f:

    # pc "Uh, hello Detective. This is [pcname]. You're working on my dad's case."
    pc "Eh, hola, detective. Soy [pcname]. Está trabajando en el caso de mi padre."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:19
translate spanish jez2_2d905853:

    # det "Right, hello. How are you?"
    det "Sí, hola. ¿Cómo estás?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:20
translate spanish jez2_0dd51ecf:

    # pc "I'm okay."
    pc "Estoy bien."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:21
translate spanish jez2_14b793aa:

    # det "Good. Well I'm sorry to say that I don't have any new information to tell you about your missing father right now."
    det "Bien. Bueno, lamento decirte que por ahora no tengo ninguna información nueva que contarte sobre tu padre desaparecido."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:22
translate spanish jez2_00a1b810:

    # pc "I'm actually calling because I think I've found a few things that could be helpful."
    pc "En realidad te llamo porque creo que he encontrado algunas cosas que podrían ser útiles."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:23
translate spanish jez2_d5d96da8:

    # det "One second. Are you okay with me recording this?"
    det "Un momento. ¿Te parece bien que grabe esto?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:24
translate spanish jez2_61f77a4c:

    # pc "Sure."
    pc "Claro."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:25
translate spanish jez2_c9df2852:

    # det "Okay, go ahead."
    det "Vale, adelante."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:26
translate spanish jez2_87db76a7:

    # pc "I searched through the basement where all my dad's work is and found a few disturbing things."
    pc "He registrado el sótano, donde está todo el trabajo de mi padre, y he encontrado algunas cosas inquietantes."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:27
translate spanish jez2_11ff4bfa:

    # pc "First of all, he had been talking to a person through e-mails who he calls Whitney. Whatever he was working on, she was involved with it."
    pc "En primer lugar, había estado hablando por correo electrónico con una persona a la que llama Whitney. Fuera lo que fuera en lo que estuviera trabajando, ella estaba involucrada."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:28
translate spanish jez2_f1d6345e:

    # det "Whitney? That doesn't match any of the names of the people he was in contact with at PQ Tech."
    det "¿Whitney? Ese nombre no coincide con ninguno de los de las personas con las que estaba en contacto en PQ Tech."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:29
translate spanish jez2_f1975034:

    # pc "No, I don't think this was for his job. This was some sort of side project he was working with her on."
    pc "No, no creo que fuera por su trabajo. Era algún tipo de proyecto paralelo en el que estaba trabajando con ella."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:30
translate spanish jez2_c928d858:

    # det "Any information about this Whitney?"
    det "¿Alguna información sobre esta Whitney?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:31
translate spanish jez2_b8024a36:

    # pc "No, I didn't find anything else about her. They were talking through e-mails and I found a laptop, but it has a password."
    pc "No, no encontré nada más sobre ella. Se comunicaban por correo electrónico y encontré un portátil, pero tiene contraseña."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:32
translate spanish jez2_21ca849d:

    # det "Okay, I'll see what we can do about that. Go on."
    det "Vale, veré qué podemos hacer al respecto. Sigue."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:33
translate spanish jez2_fe311b65:

    # pc "Okay, the next thing I found was that he was looking for a way to obtain meth."
    pc "Vale, lo siguiente que descubrí es que estaba buscando una forma de conseguir metanfetamina."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:34
translate spanish jez2_75ba73d6:

    # det "Wait, what? Your dad was on meth?"
    det "Espera, ¿qué? ¿Tu padre consumía metanfetamina?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:35
translate spanish jez2_68ecf2bc:

    # pc "I don't think so. I'd never known him to use drugs. I think he wanted it for some other reason."
    pc "No lo creo. Nunca supe que consumiera drogas. Creo que la quería por alguna otra razón."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:36
translate spanish jez2_ac7a4fa1:

    # pc "The note shows that he wanted to obtain meth to speed up his heart rate. I think it had something to do with his experiments."
    pc "La nota indica que quería conseguir metanfetamina para acelerar su ritmo cardíaco. Creo que tenía algo que ver con sus experimentos."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:37
translate spanish jez2_d569f4c6:

    # det "That opens up new possibilities for sure. I'll check around with local dealers and see if anybody saw him."
    det "Eso abre nuevas posibilidades, sin duda. Preguntaré por ahí a los traficantes locales a ver si alguien lo vio."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:38
translate spanish jez2_86553b93:

    # det "If he got mixed up with drugs around this area, that could have put him in real danger."
    det "Si se metió en líos con las drogas por esta zona, eso podría haberlo puesto en peligro real."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:39
translate spanish jez2_f1b169be:

    # pc "Yeah. It doesn't make any sense to me why he would get involved in that."
    pc "Sí. No le veo ningún sentido a que se metiera en eso."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:40
translate spanish jez2_d2bd5094:

    # det "I'm sorry. Go ahead and continue."
    det "Lo siento. Sigue, por favor."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:41
translate spanish jez2_0a1a0b4e:

    # pc "Well, apparently another thing that he needed for this experiment was a large diamond."
    pc "Bueno, al parecer otra cosa que necesitaba para este experimento era un diamante grande."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:42
translate spanish jez2_2d795a16:

    # pc "I found plans to burglarize a jewelry store."
    pc "He encontrado planes para atracar una joyería."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:43
translate spanish jez2_0107f074:

    # det "Are you fucking kidding me?"
    det "¿Me estás tomando el pelo?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:44
translate spanish jez2_830d65d5:

    # pc "No, I'm pretty sure that this is real."
    pc "No, estoy bastante seguro de que esto es real."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:45
translate spanish jez2_e2d42fe5:

    # det "Everything I've looked into about your dad shows that he's a nerdy homebody who never leaves his basement workshop."
    det "Todo lo que he investigado sobre tu padre indica que es un empollón hogareño que nunca sale de su taller del sótano."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:46
translate spanish jez2_f81b16ef:

    # det "And now you're telling me he's a meth-head diamond thief?"
    det "¿Y ahora me dices que es un adicto a la metanfetamina y ladrón de diamantes?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:47
translate spanish jez2_aea032f2:

    # pc "It doesn't make any sense, I agree."
    pc "No tiene ningún sentido, estoy de acuerdo."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:48
translate spanish jez2_07fcb2dd:

    # pc "I haven't told anybody else about this. I don't think Lisa and Suzy would even believe me."
    pc "No se lo he contado a nadie más. No creo que Lisa y Suzy me creyeran."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:49
translate spanish jez2_a07fa0f4:

    # det "I'm not sure I even believe you."
    det "Ni siquiera estoy seguro de creerte a ti."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:50
translate spanish jez2_11ce8264:

    # det "Could you take some photos of the paperwork that you found and send them to me?"
    det "¿Podrías hacer unas fotos de los papeles que has encontrado y enviármelas?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:51
translate spanish jez2_1f8345bd:

    # pc "Sure, just a sec."
    pc "Claro, un momento."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:55
translate spanish jez2_df7b0a07:

    # "I walk down to the basement and take a picture of the notes that I had found talking about the meth and the diamonds, then send them to Detective Rodriguez in a text message."
    "Bajo al sótano y hago una foto de las notas que había encontrado sobre la metanfetamina y los diamantes, y luego se las envío al detective Rodríguez por mensaje de texto."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:56
translate spanish jez2_89d815e0:

    # det "This is crazy."
    det "Esto es una locura."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:57
translate spanish jez2_c417e350:

    # pc "Yeah."
    pc "Sí."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:58
translate spanish jez2_0331d609:

    # det "Okay, take those notes and put them into an envelope or a bag or something for me and I'll come by your house and pick them up sometime soon."
    det "Vale, coge esas notas y mételas en un sobre, una bolsa o algo así, y pasaré por tu casa a recogerlas en cuanto pueda."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:59
translate spanish jez2_61f77a4c_1:

    # pc "Sure."
    pc "Claro."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:60
translate spanish jez2_83c8ee1d:

    # det "If your dad robbed a jewelry store, there should be some record of a jewelry store robbery recently. That should be easy for me to track down."
    det "Si tu padre robó una joyería, debería haber algún registro de un robo en una joyería recientemente. No debería costarme mucho localizarlo."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:61
translate spanish jez2_7f728a6b:

    # det "You did good work here, [pcname]. I'll follow up on all of this and get back to you, okay?"
    det "Has hecho un buen trabajo, [pcname]. Investigaré todo esto y te mantendré informada, ¿vale?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:62
translate spanish jez2_ae4ac277:

    # pc "Sound's good, Detective Rodriguez."
    pc "Me parece bien, detective Rodríguez."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:63
translate spanish jez2_42452d69:

    # det "Take care and let me know if you find anything else."
    det "Cuídate y avísame si encuentras algo más."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:64
translate spanish jez2_5bc44b07:

    # pc "I will."
    pc "Lo haré."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:65
translate spanish jez2_320bb728:

    # det "Okay, talk to you again soon."
    det "Vale, hablamos pronto."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:68
translate spanish jez2_0163db14:

    # "She hangs up and I walk back up to my bedroom. The ball is in her court now. Just need to wait to see what she tracks down."
    "Cuelga y yo vuelvo a mi habitación. Ahora le toca mover ficha a ella. Solo hay que esperar a ver qué descubre."

translate spanish strings:

    # game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:2
    old "Finish searching the basement."
    new "Termina de registrar el sótano."

    # game/Scenes/Jez/jez2.rpy:3
    old "Then call Detective Rodriguez from your bedroom in the evening or night."
    new "Luego llama a la detective Rodríguez desde tu habitación por la tarde o por la noche."

